data.text: To be more transparent about the grades, activities and behavior of our University’s recognized fraternities and sororities, the Office of Fraternity & Sorority Life shares the following chapter information. If you are interested in connecting with a specific chapter, feel free to visit their local or (inter)national websites. More comparative information related to chapter’s academic performance, hours volunteered, dollars donated, and conduct standing can all be found under Chapter Reports in the About tab above.
